title: Wordpress plugin - bbPress - March 2014
description:
bbPress 2.5.3 - WordPress Plugin


bbPress is forum software, made the WordPress way Have you ever been frustrated with forum or bulletin board software that was slow, bloated and always got your server hacked? bbPress is focused on ease of integration, ease of use, web standards, and speed.

WP Requirements:
3.6 or higher, up to 3.8.1

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
